Game information:

Rising Star Judo Gusiken Takahiro preparing for the match promises
to be a turning point in his career. In case of victory the athlete
became Takahiro youth national team of Japan. Despite the good availability,
Takahiro nervous. On the advice of friends, he went to the temple, which
is rumored to perform any wish or prayer. Takahiro prayed, but immediately
afterwards felt unwell and fainted. Waking up, he found himself in a
strange ancient site. Finding the way to his native village, he came
upon two girls. Girls, armed with swords, chased two girls ... foxes.
Takahiro first thought he was crazy, but then followed the girls and
got in their intrigues. Who are they and how are the upcoming Takahiro
a new world? Is time to Takahiro return to his fight?
Or he was stuck here forever?
